    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Bulbophyllum kenejiense are fever and body aches, often caused by bacterial infections treated with its antibacterial properties. The plant's anti-inflammatory compounds are effective in reducing swelling and pain associated with arthritis, a chronic condition characterized by joint inflammation and stiffness. Bulbophyllum kenejiense's antifungal properties make it a treatment option for fungal infections such as ringworm, a skin condition that affects both children and adults. By inhibiting the growth of certain bacteria, the plant helps alleviate symptoms of diarrhea, a common gastrointestinal issue often caused by bacterial contamination. Additionally, Bulbophyllum kenejiense has been shown to exhibit antiviral properties, which can help combat viral infections like the common cold and flu.",
